<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
             xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui">

    <ui:with field="res" type="com.arcbees.website.client.resources.AppResources"/>
    <ui:with field="page" type="com.arcbees.website.client.resources.PageProductResources"/>
    <ui:with field="fonts" type="com.arcbees.website.client.resources.FontResources"/>

    <g:HTMLPanel styleName="{page.style.products} {page.style.gwtp}">

        <nav class="{page.style.breadcrumb}">
            <span class="{fonts.icons.iconArcbees} {page.style.logo}"></span>
            <ul>
                <li>PRODUCT</li>
                <li>GWTP</li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">
                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_full}">
                    <h1>gwtp
                        <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="{page.style.presentation}">The best
                        <span>Model-View-Presenter</span>
                        framework for GWT
                    </h2>
                    <div class="{page.style.socialTop}">
                        <ul class="{page.style.social}">
                            <li>
                                <a href="#" class="{fonts.icons.iconGPlus}">
                                    <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Google plus</span>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <a href="#" class="{fonts.icons.iconGitHub}">
                                    <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Github</span>
                                </a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_push_1_2} {res.grid.col_m_full} {res.grid.col_m_push_0}">
                    <p>
                        <strong>GWT-Platform (GWTP) is your companion for building large web applications based on
                            Google Web
                            Toolkit (GWT).
                        </strong>
                    </p>
                    <p>Used by thousands of businesses around the world, GWTP will take your application to
                        the next level!
                    </p>
                    <p>Combining powerful features, GWTP is an out-of-the-box solution that supports all
                        the requirements of modern development. It handles the tedious work so that you can focus on
                        developing the core features of your web application, quickly and easily.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {res.style.centered}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">
                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_m_full} {res.grid.col_m_push_0}">
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.btn}">Support</a>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.btn}"><i class="{fonts.icons.iconArrowOutside}"></i>Developer's
                        Platform
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {res.style.medium2}">
            <div class="{page.style.slideshow} {res.style.wrapper}">
                <div class="{page.style.slides}">
                    <g:Image resource="{page.gwtpScreen1}"/>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="{page.style.prev}">
                    <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Prev</span>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="{page.style.next}">
                    <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Next</span>
                </a>
                <nav class="{page.style.pager} {res.style.centered}">
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <a href="#"></a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="#"></a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="#"></a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails} {res.style.centered}">
            <h2>Features</h2>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails} {res.style.medium1}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_1_3}">
                    <h3>Easy to Use Framework</h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_2_3}">
                    <p>Web applications need a solid architecture to build upon as they grow. GWTP’s
                        Model-View-Presenter (MVP) framework helps you organize your code for scalability right from the
                        start, cleanly separating the different application layers.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails} {res.style.medium2}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_1_3}">
                    <h3>Boilerplate-Free</h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_2_3}">
                    <p>GWTP harnesses the power of GWT code generation to help you reduce the amount of repetitive code
                        you need to write when building scalable applications. This frees you to focus on what matters
                        most for your application.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails} {res.style.medium3}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_1_3}">
                    <h3>Flexibility</h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_2_3}">
                    <p>GWTP was engineered with flexibility in mind. Leveraging the full power of dependency injection,
                        GWTP makes web apps more modular. By taking advantage of Google Guice and Gin, GWTP ensures you
                        have the flexibility to use all the other dependencies your application needs.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_1_3}">
                    <h3>Client/Server Communication</h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_2_3}">
                    <p>Client/Server communication is made easy using GWTP's communication libraries. The libraries
                        provided by GWTP helps you write the communication layer of your application using well-known
                        mechanisms.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails} {res.style.medium1}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_1_3}">
                    <h3>Fast</h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_2_3}">
                    <p>Big web applications can take long to load. Thankfully, GWTP comes with integrated and effortless
                        ways to cut your application's startup time. Using a technique known as code-splitting, you’ll
                        never lose a user because your application is slow.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.stripeDetails} {res.style.medium2}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_1_3}">
                    <h3>Maintenance and Evolution</h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.anchor}">#</a>
                </div>

                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_2_3}">
                    <p>With GWTP, the maintenance of your application couldn’t be easier. By letting GWTP provide the
                        framework, you reduce your maintenance workload. The strong framework also makes your app more
                        evolvable and safe to change.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {res.style.light} {res.style.centered} {page.style.moreOn}">
            <div class="{res.grid.row} {res.style.clearfix} {res.style.wrapper}">
                <div class="{res.grid.col} {res.grid.col_full}">
                    <h3>
                        <ui:msg description="All the documentations you need">more on
                        </ui:msg>

                    </h3>
                    <a href="#" class="{res.style.btn}">
                        <i class="{fonts.icons.iconArrowOutside}"></i>
                        <ui:msg description="- BTN - Go to Arcbees Developers">Developer's</ui:msg>
                        Platform
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="{res.style.stripe} {page.style.colored} {res.style.centered}">
            <h3>SHARE</h3>
            <ul class="{page.style.social}">
                <li>
                    <a href="#" class="{fonts.icons.iconFb}">
                        <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Facebook</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#" class="{fonts.icons.iconTwitter}">
                        <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Twitter</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#" class="{fonts.icons.iconGPlus}">
                        <span class="{res.style.hidden}">Google</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

    </g:HTMLPanel>
</ui:UiBinder>
